<title>USA: OUTLOOK-USDA forecast for 97/98 upland cotton.</title>
<headline>OUTLOOK-USDA forecast for 97/98 upland cotton.</headline>
<dateline>WASHINGTON 1997-02-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>USDA forecast of 1997/98 U.S. cotton output and use, compared to FAPRI and U.S. Feed Grains Council estimates and USDA for 1996/97:</p>
<p>--</p>
<p> COTTON-A		    USDA  FAPRI   USFGC   USDA</p>
<p> (Mln ac, bales)	  97/98  97/98   97/98  96/97</p>
